{"tid":2333630,"cid":36,"subCid":0,"title":"有冇人有時心情好焦急 好唔開心","createTime":"2020-12-20T14:48:28.000Z","updateTime":"2020-12-22T13:05:39.000Z","uid":86401,"like":12,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":8,"replies":[{"pid":"c38c0ae384738cf5a63dddb9ebf3f026fe0d62c7","tid":2333630,"uid":86401,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-12-20T14:48:28.000Z","msg":"平時返工對住同事係完全無事 幾有耐性都得 <br />\n但返到屋企真係忍唔住 好容易炆 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n有時屋企人講多兩句就會覺得佢地迫緊我咁 之後又搞到自己心情唔好 然後態度唔好咁回應返佢地<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n之後諗諗下 諗起自己有咩未做 同埋冇乜時間休息瞓覺 <br />\n個一刻 成個人又灰鳩咗 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n再加埋頸緊膊痛 個人唔舒服 諗起冇得休息 <br />\n間屋4個人住又嘈嘈閉想靜下都唔得個陣 <br />\n真係好撚辛苦<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/frownsmile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n啱啱又係咁 覺得好唔開心好攰 乜都唔理搞掂啲野沖左入房攤係床，開始覺得谷住谷住，好想喊<br />\n然後喊左出黎 舒服返啲 <img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n但都係唔開心同唔知焦慮啲乜春<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/upset.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n呢啲情況唔夠瞓既日子會明顯啲 <br />\n想問有冇人都有類似情況？想問下咁既情況需要搵咩人seek help 例如睇醫生之類<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"caed5b0ce40b26f4b9d67b2cd718562f5d11a105","tid":2333630,"uid":231089,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-12-20T14:54:03.000Z","msg":"同問 我係咪要睇精神科醫生<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1221a0e1e4a0a1eb0a839f229f90d813858d4d05","tid":2333630,"uid":86401,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"caed5b0ce40b26f4b9d67b2cd718562f5d11a105","tid":2333630,"uid":231089,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-12-20T14:54:03.000Z","msg":"同問 我係咪要睇精神科醫生<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-20T14:57:03.000Z","msg":"屌我都好想知<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/37.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 有冇過來人講兩句"},{"pid":"da1cd05212cabfe4ccea03238d9086461dab89f1","tid":2333630,"uid":86401,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"caed5b0ce40b26f4b9d67b2cd718562f5d11a105","tid":2333630,"uid":231089,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-12-20T14:54:03.000Z","msg":"同問 我係咪要睇精神科醫生<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-12-20T14:57:25.000Z","msg":"你係咩徵狀<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/stop.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"13d1ad2c5a0e2af499d7de54f0c61127ac522eb4","tid":2333630,"uid":231089,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"quote":{"pid":"da1cd05212cabfe4ccea03238d9086461dab89f1","tid":2333630,"uid":86401,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"caed5b0ce40b26f4b9d67b2cd718562f5d11a105","tid":2333630,"uid":231089,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-12-20T14:54:03.000Z","msg":"同問 我係咪要睇精神科醫生<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-12-20T14:57:25.000Z","msg":"你係咩徵狀<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/stop.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-12-20T14:59:39.000Z","msg":"明明冇嘢做 但突然之間勁唔開心 一做嘢就勁心急 態度就勁差 脾氣勁大 跟住出街覺得世界有少少雜音就好煩 長期出街帶耳機 但如果你要我同人講嘢都得 都會迫自己去應人<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 做人好攰 <br />\n<br />\n發最大脾氣嘅時候抌晒啲嘢落地<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />跟住個人安靜左之後又會後悔自己做嘅嘢"},{"pid":"f93958c1f5c95592c3a95b78bcb4e81f938a379a","tid":2333630,"uid":231089,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-12-20T15:00:33.000Z","msg":"仲有就係同人嘈交嘅時候會喺度喊<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />覺得自己啲嬲谷到個人就嚟爆炸 成個雞泡魚咁"},{"pid":"2067c1c1346feb21148cae0378319bea49d85b83","tid":2333630,"uid":86401,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"f93958c1f5c95592c3a95b78bcb4e81f938a379a","tid":2333630,"uid":231089,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-12-20T15:00:33.000Z","msg":"